us paid on all litres if the amount produced in one month is equal or greater to the corresponding month  months earlier  this is simply a statement by first milk that they want to encourage members to deliver more milk   another change is that the individual transporthaulage charges have been removed from st september   first milk have also stated that during the course of next week the expectation is that they will be announcing another  price rise    new board members at muller    st july  at tuesdays farmer forum meeting there were  farmers put forward for  positions on the muller farmer board   roddy catto as chairman and board member lost his position as did chris willis  grant hartman was the only one of the  candidates to retain his position and he is now joined by john hocknell and stephen foster    other places taking it to a total of  are up for election next year   at the next meeting in august the farmer forum will need to elect a chairman vice chairman and finance officer and the odds on favourite to take the position of chairman must surely be david herdman who is the current vice chairman of the group and former chairman of dcd   ppl equivalent milk price for july deliveries paid by friesland campina   th july  having announced a july farm gate price increase of  euro cents per kg wwwmilkpricescom have calculated that at current exchange rates of  euro  ppl and converted to our standard liquid litre results in a price paid of ppl  this represents an increase of ppl compared to  months ago   using the same numbers the friesland campina organic standard liquid litre price equates to a farm gate price of ppl   arla members are encouraged to discuss the proposal to move to a  months notice period    th july  arla members have been given the minimum required  working days notice to consider and express any views on the proposed resolution for the immediate removal of the  month notice to leave period to be replaced by a  month period as proposed and prom